libplcode (1.0.1-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * CTCSS (PL) tone encoder/decoder for all 50 standard tones.
  * DCS (DPL) code encoder/decoder for all 104 standard codes.
  * DTMF dual-tone encoder/decoder for all 16 symbols.
  * CW ID (Morse code) encoder/decoder.
  * MCW (Modulated CW) encoder/decoder.
  * FSK CW encoder/decoder.
  * Two-Tone Sequential Paging encoder/decoder.
  * Five-Tone Selective Call (ZVEI/CCIR/EIA) encoder/decoder.
  * MDC-1200 signaling encoder/decoder.
  * Tone burst access encoder/decoder.
  * Courtesy tone generator.
  * Golay (23,12) codec for DCS error detection.

 -- Brian West <brian@mcalester.net>  Sat, 28 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
